<h1>VoIP Software-Defined Networking Appliance.</h1>
<p class="lede">The VoiceTel SDN Appliance intelligently controls the network from the end-user's LAN and delivers unobstructed communications to the VoiceTel core, with optional in-call High Availability (HA). This is the white paper, requirements, installation, and configuration reference.</p>
